Musical chairs:
    As soon as music ends, you have to click the button, speed is accesed
    
Copy QT's Rythm:
    Qt does some simple rythm, clap clap ... clap clap clap User then has to mimic it.
    

Compare the pitches:
    QT plays some beep / sound at a certain pitch, the user has to click whether or not the new pitch is the same, or different to the previous
           Harder levels could add 2 more options "same, higher, lower"
           


